wide across eyes. Female 
<quantity box="[1217,1323,1625,1651]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.8" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" unit="mm" value="5.8">5.80 mm</quantity>
long and 
